2 <text font="1" height="13" left="225" textpieces="0" top="425" width="496">Target posts may be scarce in some detector bins. Indeed, we often have zero</text>
2 <text font="1" height="13" left="202" textpieces="0" top="443" width="519">target posts for the wildlife case study to be discussed later. This problem can</text>
