2 <text font="1" height="13" left="202" textpieces="0" top="453" width="518">number of tweets in each state-hour bin gave us z(1), from which g is estimated.</text>
2 <text font="1" height="13" left="225" textpieces="0" top="471" width="496">Figure 2 shows the estimated g. The x-axis is hour of day and y-axis is</text>
